name: Paper Planes - Comp Soc Game Jam 2016
name_original: Paper Planes - Comp Soc Game Jam 2016
description:
Winning submission of the Comp Soc Game Jam.

You have to fly a paper plane through 25 red rings to stop the clock. See how fast you can do it!

The original submission for the Comp Soc Game Jam uses the Gear VR. I am still working on it so here is a playable version for Windows.

Controls:

A/Left and D/Right arrow keys to move plane left and right.
